summary: A messy bust of Soul!Stephen because I discovered an ear piercing style that I thought looked really cool. After the Dark...
caption:
A messy bust of Soul!Stephen because I discovered an ear piercing style that I thought looked really cool.

After the Dark Dimension became his home, Stephen got some enchanted piercings to make himself look meaner help him adjust to the shift in dimensional energy. He also sharpened his teeth and pointed his ears using magic as a sort of symbolic representation for the loss of his humanity. you don’t want to be labelled as “that one human” in public, unless you want to get knifed over a market stall.

Half the people think Clea just keeps him as her bitch an exotic pet, rather than actually being married to him.  He’s fine with it, so long as they don’t mess with his queen.

title: What Holds Me Together
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2zUTkwi

by ItsumiLucy

Tony knew deep in his gut that he shouldn’t have taken him along with them. It wasn’t suppose to go like this at all. Sure, people around him got hurt all the time and he’d be lying if he said it didn’t hurt every time, but this, this was something so much harder to him. No matter how many times he’s had to do it now.

Or

summary: I believe everything has limits. I do like children, I know how to look after them, I had to help raise my little brother and my...
body:
I believe everything has limits. I do like children, I know how to look after them, I had to help raise my little brother and my little sister after all, nothing against children, they’re amazing. However, do not expect me to tolerate bullying and rudeness because I don’t. I’m good at keeping my cool but that doesn’t mean my patience is eternal. I don’t think I’m “great” with children, but I don’t think I’m bad either.

Some kids are angels to be around, others are little monsters, don’t expect me to let them pull my hair and make fun of me because I won’t allow that.

…

…
